ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectContributions to assist livestock producers in Alberta and Saskatchewan
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to provide for FEDERAL CONTRIBUTIONS OF UP TO $10,000,000 TO ASSIST LIVESTOCK PRODUCERS in ALBERTA and SASKATCHEWAN who are faced with the extraordinary costs related to the discovery of bovine tuberculosis in the fall of 2016.
